[Text engl]
{Name}{}{Alan}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see Alan.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{This is definetely a guy, but there is something feminine in him.}
{Speech 1}{}{Преддиалоговые установки}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{-}
{Speech 2}{}{What do you need from Alan?}
